query: Show me data about business units and segments
sql:
SELECT
    cisco_stage_app.metrics.business_unit_id, cisco_stage_app.metrics.segment_id, cisco_stage_app.metrics.metric_value, cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics.linearity_score, cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside.qtd_commit, cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics.funnel_stage
FROM cisco_stage_app.metrics
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics
    ON cisco_stage_app.metrics.business_unit_id = cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics.business_unit_id
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside
    ON cisco_stage_app.metrics.segment_id = cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside.segment_id
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics
    ON cisco_stage_app.metrics.business_unit_id = cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics.business_unit_id
